{"tid":297950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣逼男朋友減肥","createTime":"2017-06-26T01:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T04:26:31.000Z","uid":25070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b627b18fb6853f000fa2f35e3514104358723f","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:27:41.000Z","msg":"佢170高，73kg，睇落都唔算勁肥<br />\n不過有超大個肚腩<br />\n成隻小熊維尼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢平時食飯會食兩三碗<br />\n又鍾意食M記<br />\n一熱就想飲凍野，食雪糕<br />\n最大問題係好鍾意飲飲品<br />\n凍檸茶，凍奶茶，飲好快好大量<br />\n紙包飲品當水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實佢自己都話想減，但冇時間做運動(返夜校)<br />\n我話咁可以由飲食開始做起先，佢又話忍唔到口<br />\n我試過開個條件，佢減到十磅，我就送個願望俾佢，乜都得<br />\n佢都話冇乜想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拿，我真係唔係嫌佢肥<br />\n我真係擔心佢健康架<br />\n佢咁唔控制飲食 我真係好驚佢會有糖尿病果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點先可以令佢有決心減肥呀？"},{"pid":"838551386e0b10d8d16a43b9ceb936a3dfcca42c","tid":297950,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:33:31.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊增肥 ，咁你咪明白佢感受"},{"pid":"48ea714ccbcd13991f5013f100395d781a2a069b","tid":297950,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:42:13.000Z","msg":"上youtude搵關於健康嘅片<br />\n日日播俾佢睇洗佢腦<br />\n要嚴厲啲,健康唔係講玩<br />\n你男朋友咁食法唔夠60就打柴<br />\n如果你想同佢過世你就要下決心"},{"pid":"48c5f2f4d2961a677b005bfbf9acff21eed8a030","tid":297950,"uid":42138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"44060d7db9e4a274f118007a444681601325a106","tid":297950,"uid":98884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:47:17.000Z","msg":"你增肥增到佢嫌你肥..再一齊去做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9850d95905a65a06d2505020753f27f6c712414","tid":297950,"uid":109726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"分左手佢就會減架啦<br />\n利申:135減到110"},{"pid":"faece3b1541076e272912965e685ecedcb839354","tid":297950,"uid":75464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手佢就會減架啦<br />\n利申:135減到110</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 無咩野打擊自己 係唔會有決心 會安於現況"},{"pid":"ed6dce79c0f611d8bccee0b92cb611028a2ab4f0","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:58:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢一齊增肥 ，咁你咪明白佢感受</blockquote><br />\n我明白減肥係好辛苦的，我自己都減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7840084559a529e5da8efb9d9cbef1e94873a675","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上youtude搵關於健康嘅片<br />\n日日播俾佢睇洗佢腦<br />\n要嚴厲啲,健康唔係講玩<br />\n你男朋友咁食法唔夠60就打柴<br />\n如果你想同佢過世你就要下決心</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打意見，我會試下"},{"pid":"7b3deed4049893a51ec281bbda98d90d66e7361b","tid":297950,"uid":8799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手佢就會減架啦<br />\n利申:135減到110</blockquote><br />\n無錯<br />\n利申 分左手瘦左廿磅"},{"pid":"7451d01e037831ff5d152dc2a5aaf39f11a3092b","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>分左手佢就會減架啦<br />\n利申:135減到110</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 無咩野打擊自己 係唔會有決心 會安於現況</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要玩到咁大，好驚佢覺得我嫌棄佢"},{"pid":"cfb2df03ade027bf29273d18229f30b971cf732f","tid":297950,"uid":35993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:04:22.000Z","msg":"我都俾女朋友嫌我肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />百三磅，全部去哂個肚腩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b70be82187353252f790589ffce528d957c174","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都俾女朋友嫌我肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />百三磅，全部去哂個肚腩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係佢擔心健康架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打有冇諗住減肥，<br />\n女友有冇做d咩推動你減肥"},{"pid":"c931a77b14945193f915070524687b21bc65844b","tid":297950,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:10:55.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊做gym<br />\n一星期2-3次<br />\n1次1.5小時左右"},{"pid":"e2bfb2c710bf65fb6016521fd3aeff87f6040a9d","tid":297950,"uid":120427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"先控制唔好飲咁多甜嘢啦，凍都ok,甜嘅飲品係大肚腩原凶<br />\n<a href=\"https://authoritynutrition.com/13-ways-sugary-soda-is-bad-for-you/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauthoritynutrition.com%2F13-ways-sugary-soda-is-bad-for-you%2F&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0f83accf\" target=\"_blank\">https://authoritynutrition.com/13-ways-sugary-soda-is-bad-for-you/</a>"},{"pid":"c01e22478a4d0c9aae59958ea53d2066def9aba7","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢一齊做gym<br />\n一星期2-3次<br />\n1次1.5小時左右</blockquote><br />\n其實有引佢做運動<br />\n琴日都想同佢行山，咁好天<br />\n但佢話冇mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊會嚴厲d，捉佢落街跑步"},{"pid":"811936d9a44e422122e72407d9506c3f8d05cafc","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先控制唔好飲咁多甜嘢啦，凍都ok,甜嘅飲品係大肚腩原凶<br />\n<a href=\"https://authoritynutrition.com/13-ways-sugary-soda-is-bad-for-you/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauthoritynutrition.com%2F13-ways-sugary-soda-is-bad-for-you%2F&d=cqr16t5r9tUJDj39CKmzKm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0f83accf\" target=\"_blank\">https://authoritynutrition.com/13-ways-sugary-soda-is-bad-for-you/</a></blockquote><br />\n呢個真，我已經成日逼佢飲水<br />\n同我一齊佢都唔俾佢飲甜野<br />\n但我冇同佢一齊時，我唔知佢有冇偷飲<br />\n真係睇唔到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d02e9d7fd04aba4360a8955bf71dd3d7640d4c","tid":297950,"uid":84272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"我明你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我男友18x高 但200磅......"},{"pid":"2825889471abcc91c1f271e31a29425778c66f58","tid":297950,"uid":35993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都俾女朋友嫌我肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />百三磅，全部去哂個肚腩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係佢擔心健康架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打有冇諗住減肥，<br />\n女友有冇做d咩推動你減肥</blockquote><br />\n依家每日都十二點前瞓，戒凍飲，平時飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfac2febec6e1d4f0692fc547bda8348e4a7e81","tid":297950,"uid":81439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"唔減冇得扑<br />\n再唔減分手"},{"pid":"49e915bd5b1afa9a1d086641d11f3b551418b4c9","tid":297950,"uid":29620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:59:08.000Z","msg":"日日同佢扑野<br />\n每次4,5Q<br />\n一個月後包變人乾"},{"pid":"aca39b42db2a9641818782210fe44fb9ed94d53b","tid":297950,"uid":62830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"咁唔係肥唔肥問題啦，根本命都唔長"},{"pid":"5c22a8b9468d9f29a8e33e4adade577f07b23250","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都俾女朋友嫌我肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />百三磅，全部去哂個肚腩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係佢擔心健康架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打有冇諗住減肥，<br />\n女友有冇做d咩推動你減肥</blockquote><br />\n依家每日都十二點前瞓，戒凍飲，平時飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打都有決心，希望逼到佢戒飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3581fb51658fcd561236bfd101a9936dc4339509","tid":297950,"uid":25070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁唔係肥唔肥問題啦，根本命都唔長</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以好想佢會改下飲食習慣<br />\n其實佢以前都係瘦底，但太放縱係咁食<br />\n又冇決心，成日話食大左個胃，唔夠飽<br />\n係咁俾藉口自己，我除左日日講話佢唔健康<br />\n都唔知可以做d乜，講太多又驚佢嫌我煩/覺得我嫌棄佢"},{"pid":"99d94d573b44abfd3008ebc567212a608984bed4","tid":297950,"uid":35993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都俾女朋友嫌我肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />百三磅，全部去哂個肚腩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係佢擔心健康架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打有冇諗住減肥，<br />\n女友有冇做d咩推動你減肥</blockquote><br />\n依家每日都十二點前瞓，戒凍飲，平時飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打都有決心，希望逼到佢戒飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同佢出街嗰陣買水，食飯唔俾佢飲凍嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}